several times over, and staff with stock options, staff who owned shares in the company,

00:04:38.815 --> 00:04:44.945
as well as early investors, would receive a bumper payday, they would make a load of money.

00:04:45.955 --> 00:04:53.285
Yet, over the period of a few weeks WeWork fell from the stars, as investors looked more

00:04:53.285 --> 00:05:00.405
closely at the company and smelled something fishy, they felt that something was wrong.

00:05:01.725 --> 00:05:07.065
